  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-medium text-heading">Overview</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        SmartyPantz Escape Rooms was the first escape room experience provider in Gastown, located in the heart of Vancouver. As pioneers in the local escape room market, they needed a brand positioning strategy that would cement their first-mover advantage and establish them as the go-to destination for immersive entertainment in the city.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Challenge -->
  <section class="bg-bg-light px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-medium text-heading">The Challenge</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        As the escape room industry grew rapidly in Vancouver, SmartyPantz faced the challenge of standing out in an increasingly competitive market. New competitors were entering the space regularly, and the brand needed to differentiate itself beyond simply being "the first." They needed a strategy that would communicate their unique value proposition and keep them top-of-mind with both locals and tourists visiting Gastown.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-medium text-heading">Our Approach</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        We developed a comprehensive brand strategy that leveraged SmartyPantz's unique position as Gastown's original escape room provider. Our approach focused on the rich heritage of the Gastown location, the authenticity of being the first-mover in the market, and the quality of their immersive experiences. We crafted messaging that connected the historic charm of Gastown with the excitement of escape room adventures, creating a brand narrative that no competitor could replicate.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results -->
  <section class="bg-bg-light px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-medium text-heading">Results</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        The refreshed brand strategy delivered measurable results for SmartyPantz. Brand recognition increased significantly across Vancouver, and customer engagement saw a marked improvement. The positioning as Gastown's original escape room experience resonated strongly with both new and returning visitors, helping SmartyPantz maintain its leadership position in the local market.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

